responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D488408C4D58B073545ABF8DC40A7E3E", "Excellent! From my personal records, I have divulged that there was a secret society of kyrons devoted to purging the land when first this plague emerged from the darkness. Find them and I may find the formula for the cure. You hunt begins in the history of the Aelan Empire. Seek the records of the Fall of the Aelan Empire. There we will find answers. May Kyron Keep You!  ")
